item.description:
Meet the artists in Natick!!

Be a part of a series of art-inspired networking events. Discuss asethetic, craft and talent by crawling with fellow artists and architects as part of larger open artist studio events. After visiting local studios, the party will head somewhere nearby for food or drinks. If you can't make the party, you can visit the Natick studios from October 16 - 17, 12-5pm.

Meet outside Bakery on the Common (9 South Main St.) at 2:30 pm

For more information contact Rebecca McWilliams at rmcwilliams[at]smma.com.
item.how_to_find_us: Meet out front of the Bakery at 2:30 pm.
item.name: Architects and Artists Collaborate: Natick Open Studios Crawl
